{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "62bdd814-aa07-483d-880c-846b251899e0",
    "name": "Sport AI API - Backend",
    "description": "Collection para testar a API inicial de upload, processamento, extracao de frames, deteccao de pose, metricas biomecanicas, analise temporal, scoring e feedback da Sport AI Platform.\n\nAntes de executar, inicie o backend em http://localhost:8000.\n\nNo request de upload, selecione manualmente um arquivo de video valido no campo `file`. Ao concluir um upload com sucesso, o `videoId` retornado sera salvo automaticamente na variavel da collection e utilizado nos requests seguintes. Execute `Extract Frames` e `Detect Pose` antes de `Calculate Metrics` e `Analyze Movement`; execute `Analyze Movement` antes de `Calculate Score`; execute `Calculate Score` antes de `Generate Feedback`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "health"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Verifica se a API esta respondendo."
      },
      "response": [],
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Health check retorna 200\", function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "",
              "pm.test(\"Status da API esta ok\", function () {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().status).to.eql(\"ok\");",
              "});"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "packages": {}
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Videos",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload Video",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "file",
                  "description": "Selecione um video mp4, mov, avi, mkv ou webm de ate 200 MB.",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": []
                },
                {
                  "key": "exerciseType",
                  "value": "squat",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "cameraView",
                  "value": "side",
                  "description": "Use front para video frontal ou side para video lateral.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/videos/upload",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "videos",
                "upload"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Envia um arquivo de video no campo multipart/form-data `file`, com `exerciseType=squat` e `cameraView=front|side`."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Upload retorna 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"videoId\", body.videoId);",
                  "",
                  "    pm.test(\"Resposta inclui videoId\", function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(body.videoId).to.be.a(\"string\").and.not.empty;",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "packages": {}
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Video Info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/videos/{{videoId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
